<main>
  <section class="start-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Getting Started</div>
      <h1 class="headline-lg">How to Start with Payxem</h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle">From signup to your first payment in under 60 seconds. No monthly fees. No complexity.</p>
      <div class="start-screenshot">
        <img src="/images/0 start  main app-page.png" alt="Payxem app dashboard showing wallet balance, invoices, and earnings" loading="eager">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">1</div>
        <h2>Create Your Free Account</h2>
        <p>Sign up at <a href="https://app.payxem.com">app.payxem.com</a> using your email. No credit card needed. No monthly fees. You will receive a magic link to verify your email and log in securely.</p>
        <div class="start-screenshot-row">
          <img src="/images/start 1 -Payxem_Login-signup.jpg" alt="Payxem signup and login screen" loading="lazy">
          <img src="/images/start 2 magic link.jpg" alt="Payxem magic link login sent to email" loading="lazy">
          <img src="/images/start 3 payxem email link.jpg" alt="Payxem magic link email with sign in button" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">2</div>
        <h2>Set Your PIN</h2>
        <p>After signing in, set a secure PIN for quick access to your dashboard. You can also enable biometric login (fingerprint or face recognition) for faster access.</p>
        <div class="start-screenshot">
          <img src="/images/start 4 - set PIN.png" alt="Payxem set PIN screen for secure quick access" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">3</div>
        <h2>Complete Your Profile</h2>
        <p>Add your business name, service type, and location. This information appears on your invoices and helps clients trust you.</p>
        <div class="start-screenshot">
          <img src="/images/start 5 Payxem_Profile_scr.jpg" alt="Payxem profile setup screen with business details" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">4</div>
        <h2>Set Up Your Payout Method</h2>
        <p>Go to your profile and add either:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Bank account</strong> (IBAN, account title, bank name) for local withdrawals</li>
          <li><strong>Crypto wallet</strong> (USDT address and chain) for fast international transfers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">5</div>
        <h2>Verify Your Identity</h2>
        <p>Complete KYC verification to unlock withdrawals and higher limits. The process takes a few minutes through our verification partner. You will need a valid government ID.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">6</div>
        <h2>Send Your First Invoice</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Tap <strong>Create Invoice</strong> from your dashboard</li>
          <li>Enter your client's email</li>
          <li>Add line items with description, quantity, and price</li>
          <li>Set a due date</li>
          <li>Choose whether to pass the processing fee to your client (optional)</li>
          <li>Hit <strong>Send</strong></li>
        </ol>
        <p>Your client receives a professional email with a <strong>Pay Now</strong> button. They can pay using PayPal, credit/debit card, or cryptocurrency.</p>
        <div class="start-screenshot">
          <img src="/images/start 6 Invoice create.png" alt="Payxem invoice creation screen with line items and payment link" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">7</div>
        <h2>Or Use a Payment Link</h2>
        <p>Not every job needs a full invoice. Create a <strong>Service Link</strong> with a fixed amount and a custom URL like <strong>app.payxem.com/p/yourname</strong>. Share it anywhere. Clients click, pay, done.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">8</div>
        <h2>Track Your Earnings</h2>
        <p>Your dashboard shows everything in one place:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Pending balance</strong> (payments in hold period)</li>
          <li><strong>Available balance</strong> (ready to withdraw)</li>
          <li><strong>Transaction history</strong> with fee breakdowns</li>
          <li><strong>Invoice status</strong> (draft, sent, paid, completed)</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="start-screenshot">
          <img src="/images/start 7 payxem-wallet.png" alt="Payxem wallet and ledger showing balance, transactions, and earnings" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">9</div>
        <h2>Withdraw Your Money</h2>
        <p>Once your balance is available, request a payout to your bank account or crypto wallet. Withdrawals are free with standard processing. Admin reviews and approves within 1-2 business days.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">10</div>
        <h2>Earn XEM Reward Points</h2>
        <p>You earn XEM points on every transaction, milestone, and referral. Redeem XEM for account credit to reduce your costs. The more you use Payxem, the more you save.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="start-section-inner">
        <div class="start-step-number">?</div>
        <h2>Need Help?</h2>
        <p>Tap the chat icon to talk to <strong>XemGen</strong>, our AI assistant. It understands your account, answers questions about fees, payments, and features, and responds in your language (Urdu, Hinglish, and English).</p>

        <div class="start-summary">
          <p>Sign up (60 seconds) → Complete profile → Send invoice → Get paid → Withdraw. No monthly fees. You only pay 3.5% + $0.30 when you receive a payment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <h2 class="headline-lg">Ready to Get Paid?</h2>
        <p>Create your free account, send your first invoice, and start collecting payments today.</p>
        <a href="https://app.payxem.com" class="btn btn-white btn-lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Create Free Account
          <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 10a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h10.638L10.23 5.29a.75.75 0 111.04-1.08l5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 010 1.08l-5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 11-1.04-1.08l4.158-3.96H3.75A.75.75 0 013 10z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        </a>
        <p class="cta-note">No credit card required. Start in under 60 seconds.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
